&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic , committed band 5 nurse to join our dynamic, friendly team on the Acute Medical Assessment Unit. It&#39;s a busy unit which cares for patients with a range of medical conditions and receives on average 40 patients per day. The successful applicant will be given the opportunity to develop skills in the triage, assessment and management of patients who are acutely unwell whilst working within a supportive environment. We offer a comprehensive preceptorship programme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 10 November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
